/*
 * $Id: ChangeLog,v 1.3679 2004/12/17 10:58:10 aleytys Exp $
 */

/* Use this format for the entry headers:
   YYYY-MM-DD HH:MM UTC[-|+]hhmm Your Full Name <your_email@address>
   For example:
   2002-12-01 23:12 UTC+0100 Foo Bar <foo.bar@foobar.org>
*/

2004-12-17 14:14 UTC+0100 Giancarlo Niccolai <gc at niccolai dot ws>
  * source/vm/hash.c
    ! HGetValues() was retriving keys instead of values on flat hashes.
      Funny; I am quite sure this worked a while ago.

2004-12-17 10:50 UTC+0000 Philip Chee <philip@aleytys.pc.my>
  + source\ct\setkeys.prg
    + SAVESETKEYS(), RESTSETKEYS()
