2004-12-08 21:45 UTC-0300 Eduardo Fernandes <modalsit@yahoo.com.br>

  * utils/hbmake/hbmake.prg
  * utils/hbmake/hbmutils.prg
    + HbCT.lib was added into default libs and removed from external libs.

  * source/ct/util.prg
    - removed WhatWin() function. This function should be replaced by
      the new OS_IsWinXXXX() functions suplied by Peter Rees.

  * source/ct/diskutil.prg
    * diskformat function was reviewed to use the new OS_IsWinXXXX() functions,
      instead old WhatWin() function. The diskformat function was modified to
      accept the same parameters that original diskformat CT function, but
      only for call compatibility. See notes.
    * diskfree(), disktotal() and diskused() functions were reviewed.

  * doc/en/ct/util.txt
  * doc/en/ct/diskutil.txt
    * revised to the changes made above.

  * doc/en/ct/*.txt
    * all docs was reviewed to change CT3 and LibCT name category to HBCT name.

2004-12-09 09:10 UTC+1200 Peter Rees <peter(AT)rees.co.nz>
  * contrib/what32/source/_windir.c
    - remove => #define _WIN32_WINNT   0x0500
    * HB_FUNC( GETVOLUMEPATHNAME )
        use GetProcAddress() to allow use on older Windows

