2004-12-06 00:30 UTC+0100 Henryk Olkowski <oh1@op.pl>
  * source/rtl/gtapi.c
   ! fixed hb_gtwrite()
   ! fixed hb_gtwriteAT()
     Problem:
      @ 0,0 say replicate("*",maxcol()+5)
      x:=row(); y:=col()
      ? x,y
     Result in Clipper 5.3b linking without ctus.obj and ct53.lib
      0 84
     Result in Clipper 5.3b linking with ctus.obj and ct53.lib
      1 0
     Temporary solution for xHarbour
      - if not use WOPEN() result: 0 84
      - after use WOPEN() result:  1 0

2004-12-05 17:24 UTC-0600 Vicente Guerra <vicente@guerra.com.mx>
  * bin/bld.bat
    * hbzip.lib will only be linked if the file (hbzip.lib) exist.

