2004-11-26 21:58 UTC+0600 Vicente Guerra <vicente@guerra.com.mx>
  * source/rtl/gtwin/gtwin.c
    - Commented out the "Under Win98, Upper row keys are affected by
      caps-lock and should not be" fix. This is code works only for
      US keyboard layout. Using non-US keyboards, keystrokes are
      wrong "recognized".

