  * source/rtl/gtwin/gtwin.c
    * OSVERSIONINFO structure moved to a static variable.
    + Added altgr_key item into tag_ClipKeyCode, for avoid conflicts
      with characters typed with AltGr in foregin keyboards.
    * "Upper row keys" hack under Win98 is only performed on Win9x
      environment.

2004-11-25 14:00 UTC-0300 Mauricio Abre <maurifull@datafull.com>
  * include/gfx.ch
