    + gfxSetClip() translate
  * source/rtl/gtalleg/gtalleg.c
    + GFX_SETCLIP implementation
    + gfx API ability to get buffered under dispBegin()/dispEnd()

2004-11-25 16:15 UTC+0100 Maurilio Longo <maurilio.longo@libero.it>
  * source/rtl/tbrowse.prg
    ! Fixed ::PosCursor() to keep track of centered/right-justified
      columns. Fixed ::Dehilite(), had the same error of ::Hilite()
      previously fixed.
      Fixed coloring of columns when a column's colorblock returns
      an empty array and then fixed coloring of header/footers
      which should use CLR_STANDARD (as per clipper docs) and as
      a sample on news.xharbour.org shows when compiled under clipper.

