2004-11-24 11:28 UTC+0100 Maurilio Longo <maurilio.longo@libero.it>
  * source/rtl/tbrowse.prg
    ! fixed ::Hilite() method which was calling ::DispCell() with wrong
      parameters. Removed redundant logic to test if current cell is
      inside ::ColorRect() bounds. This completely fixes news.xharbour.org
      reported slowness when painting a cursor which extends to a full row.

