    * casting
    + added .prg definition: __PLATFORM__UNIX - which is common for
      all *nixes to avoid redunt definitions for __PLATFORM__Linux,
      __PLATFORM__BSD, __PLATFORM__Darwin, __PLATFORM__SunOS, ...
    * added new .prg definitions: __ARCH{16|32|64}BIT__,
      __{LITTLE|BIG|PDP}_ENDIAN__ - they are set to sizeof( void * )

